														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1450468">
									

<p>Gotta say, I really like the idea behind fringe theories, but it needs more meat to work, particularly as a 001. The mechanism is really fuzzy (not memetic, but seems to behave similarly?), and the punchline is really abrupt. There need to be a few more O5-classified big-reveals, and they need to be have bit more impact. Perhaps start with theories that spawned individual SCPs, then build up to&#8230;. something. I would like to see this brought to fruition; thoughts?</p>

							</div>

								
					
